e learn more for schools universities and corporations  groups of  or more can participate in tailormade group trips in any destination most projects can be customized to fit the goals of a group and the needs of the local communities in which we work learn more learn more bring your children on the family trip of a lifetime  in most destinations children under  years old can accompany their parents on our projects to volunteer abroad together as a family learn more learn more contact us chat online with a program advisor apply now contact us contact us submit chat online with a program advisor get a free brochure subscribe to our newsletter apply now recently viewed by others morocco tamazight language courses vietnam psychologist pro cambodia khmer project standard south africa general care projects standard tanzania medicine standard as seen in media tell your friends about this page share google  tweet email back to top ▲